Installed-Size: 272036
Description: Unofficial iOS jailbreak port of OpenAI Codex CLI — local coding agent (Rust TUI).
 Repackaged for jailbroken iOS (Dopamine / Procursus) by tg@xauszulay. This is NOT an official
 OpenAI build; the upstream Codex CLI (github.com/openai/codex, Apache-2.0) is cross-compiled to
 aarch64-apple-ios and dropped into a self-contained, PATH-independent install under
 /var/jb/usr/local/lib/codex with a wrapper at /var/jb/usr/local/bin/codex. A bundled Node
 runtime (arm64-ios) is included only for the auth helper and the optional JS launcher fallback.
 Adds the `codex` command to NewTerm 3 / zsh with no extra configuration.
 Includes a Settings.app pane (PreferenceLoader) to pick the model, sandbox, approval policy,
 web search, fast mode, memories and log level, plus action buttons (open config/logs, reset
 auth, run diagnostics) without editing config.toml.
Homepage: https://github.com/xauszulay/codex-ios
